edu.umd.cs.psl.model.predicate

Class FunctionalPredicate

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.psl.model.predicate.Predicate
      • edu.umd.cs.psl.model.predicate.FunctionalPredicate
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExternalFunctionalPredicate, SpecialPredicate

    public abstract class FunctionalPredicate
extends Predicate
    A Predicate with GroundAtoms that have truth values defined by a function of their arguments and the ObservedAtoms of the closed StandardPredicates of the GroundAtoms' Databases.

    Before extending this class, users should consider using a SpecialPredicate or an ExternalFunctionalPredicate.
